<a data-tip="p$t$shi-ming-76" href="/people/shi-ming-76">施眠</a>，<strong title="看着我的眼睛" class="zu-question-my-bio">看着我的眼睛</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="772">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$he-jian-ge-nian" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/he-jian-ge-nian" class="zg-link" title="鹤见歌年">鹤见歌年</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xu-xiao-jiong-89-53" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xu-xiao-jiong-89-53" class="zg-link" title="徐小囧">徐小囧</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wei-en-da-shu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wei-en-da-shu" class="zg-link" title="韦恩大叔">韦恩大叔</a></span>
